# Minimize the build context: the Dockerfile needs go.mod, go.sum, *.go, and
# the build-time smoke test (tests/smoke.sh, run in the `test` stage). Deny
# everything, then allow only those inputs back in so a stray
# keys.txt / .env / .env.dec in the working tree never reaches the daemon.
*
!go.mod
!go.sum
!*.go
!tests
!tests/smoke.sh
